@startuml c-activity-swa-phase-c-application-workflow-v1
title Phase C — SwA Application Workflow Net

skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor AliceBlue
  BorderColor SteelBlue
  DiamondBackgroundColor LightYellow
  DiamondBorderColor DarkGoldenrod
  ArrowColor SteelBlue
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam swimlane {
  BorderColor CadetBlue
  TitleFontStyle bold
}

|Software Architect / PE|
start
:Step 0.L Query learnings
(query_learnings);
:Discovery Scan Step 0
(read BA, RR, SCO, DA draft);
:Derive APP/ASV/IFC entities
from BA BSV/BPR/BFN;
:Author cross-layer mappings
(ASV->BPR, ASV->BSV);

if (Missing business detail?) then (yes)
  :Raise bounded CQ;
  |Project Manager|
  :Route CQ to PO/User;
  |User|
  :Answer CQ;
  |Software Architect / PE|
  :Integrate answer and continue;
else (no)
endif

:Produce runtime-scoped archimate-application and
interaction views;
:Run model verification;
:Create Phase C handoff for PM + CSCO;

|Project Manager|
:Evaluate gate readiness
for Phase C baseline;
stop
